data.description: Step into luxury living with this impeccably crafted 2019 home boasting a stunning gourmet kitchen complete with granite countertops, sleek cabinetry, and a convenient breakfast bar. Entertain effortlessly in the spacious living room accented by a cozy gas fireplace. Host elegant dinners in the separate dining room while enjoying the warmth of family gatherings. Retreat to the main level primary suite featuring a tray ceiling, dual walk-in closets, and a luxurious en-suite bathroom with double vanities, a walk-in shower, and a sumptuous soaking tub. Upstairs, discover a versatile loft space ideal for study sessions, playtime, or transforming into your dream home office or theater. Additional spacious bedrooms offer comfort and privacy for every family member. Nestled in the prestigious Hollowstone subdivision, enjoy exclusive access to amenities such as swimming, tennis, and a playground. With easy access to Hwy 78, Grayson High School, shopping, dining, and the serene Vines Park, this home offers the perfect blend of convenience and luxury living. Don't miss your chance to call this exquisite property home!
